<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٥٥٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6952">يَحْيَى بْنُ بُكَيْرٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5348">اللَّيْثُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5287">كَثِيرِ بْنِ فَرْقَدٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ: </a>أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنَ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> أَخْبَرَهُ قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كَانَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَذْبَحُ وَيَنْحَرُ بِالْمُصَلَّى.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>